    {
        "content": "<p>if you just want some way to solve it, <code>rw [show f (g b) = (f ∘ g) b from rfl, h, id.def]</code>. I don't know that there's anything like <code>nth_rewrite</code> or <code>occs</code> in lean4 (my light skim suggests not), though; you could also try something like <code>rw [←hb, show f (g (id b)) = (f ∘ g) b from rfl, h]</code> but that's still just workarounds</p>",
